~ EnemySpikeTutorial
Now the opponent has spiked the ball.
The yellow, dome shaped marker on the sand shows where the ball will land.
You are once again controlling the receiver.
Use the A and D keys to move to where the ball will land.
Remember the receive?
Once you are at the right location, you can press the W key once the ball gets close to the receiver to receive the ball!
Don't worry if you mess up the first time; you will get to try multiple times here.
do end_dialogue()